{
  "stem": "22840.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Relatively to me, he was old.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He looked to me old.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It may have been the second wave of Wehrmacht This was 1945-- '44, '45.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Germany was over.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "This was the remnants of the Germans.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He may have been old.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He-- he-- he showed me how a rifle works, and how a Schmeisser-- Schmeisser is the submachine gun that the Germans used-- how a Schmeisser works and how a grenade works, what is a grenade.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Very friendly.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He didn't know I'm Jewish, I'm sure.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And, and the most thing which I learned is how to dread the people who are really the cruelest.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They were not the Germans.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They were the Ukrainians.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "There was a Ukrainian contingent fighting with the German Army.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They were under the command of General Vlasov.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We called them the Vlasovtsy, the people of Vlasov.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] They were the cruel ones.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "They were the ones that-- that killed and maimed, that-- that hit, that-- that were undisciplined.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "The Germans, even the SS, was clearly, even for a child in my recollection, were a disciplined army unit, or an SS unit.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "They killed, possibly with passion, when they were told to kill.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I don't think they would kill on a whim.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "They would execute.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "They would burn.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "They would-- but they did.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And I'll come to it in a moment.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "But the Vlasovsty were the cruel ones.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "The Vlasovsty were the people-- I'll-- I'll give you one episode.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] This place was [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] in the mountains.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "I'll show you pictures.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] It was not a road, not a main road.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "It was on a road which went from Donovaly to nowhere.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "It was not a strategic road.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "It didn't lead to any place.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
